item.title: My First Post
item.description: Intro to a brand new post This is my first post. I have created this post to share my thoughts and views on a variety of topics. Most especially tecchnology, programming, and the future of the world. I like to program mostly in Go, Javascript and Python. I am a Full Stack Developer and I am always looking for new ways to improve my skills and knowledge. I like to do most of my work in Linux and Windows.
